 Fury concluded': Trump aide declares 'objectives achieved' in Iran action]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130842075.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/operation-epic-fury-concluded-trump-aide-declares-objectives-achieved-in-iran-action/articleshow/130842075.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/operation-epic-fury-concluded-trump-aide-declares-objectives-achieved-in-iran-action/articleshow/130842075.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-06T07:27:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130842093,imgsize-871979.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Twitch streamer Amouranth hides for safety as gunfire breaks out near her house, chilling footage surfaces online]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130841547.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Kaitlyn Siragusa revealed that multiple gunshots were fired outside her home, forcing her to barricade herself inside. She told fans there was “lots of gunfire outside right now” and later confirmed she was “barricaded down and safe for now.” Security footage showed a hooded figure nearby, though involvement remains unclear. The incident has renewed concerns about her safety following past stalking and home invasion threats.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/twitch-streamer-amouranth-hides-for-safety-as-gunfire-breaks-out-near-her-house-chilling-footage-surfaces-online/articleshow/130841547.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/twitch-streamer-amouranth-hides-for-safety-as-gunfire-breaks-out-near-her-house-chilling-footage-surfaces-online/articleshow/130841547.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-06T05:47:26+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130841547,imgsize-37244.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Not sure if I will live": Candace Owens drops chilling texts as Charlie Kirk feared for his life before death]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130841469.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens shared alleged messages from Charlie Kirk claiming he feared for his life before his death. In the texts, Kirk spoke about being “wiped out” and said, “Anyway, I am not sure if I will live to see the end of this revolution.” Owens expressed regret for dismissing his concerns and hinted at a possible cover-up, though she provided no verified evidence to support the claim.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/not-sure-if-i-will-live-candace-owens-drops-chilling-texts-as-charlie-kirk-feared-for-his-life-before-death/articleshow/130841469.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/not-sure-if-i-will-live-candace-owens-drops-chilling-texts-as-charlie-kirk-feared-for-his-life-before-death/articleshow/130841469.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-06T05:25:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130841469,imgsize-52312.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the Day by Usain Bolt: 'I don’t think limits' words of inspiration from the fastest man on Earth]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130841476.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Usain Bolt’s quote, “I don’t think limits,” reflects a mindset shaped by injuries, setbacks, and discipline throughout his career. Beyond sprinting, it challenges people to resist early self-imposed ceilings, rethink what’s possible, and focus on solutions over judgment. Bolt’s approach emphasizes consistent effort, mental resilience, and refusing to let temporary setbacks define long-term potential, both on and off the track.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/quote-of-the-day-by-usain-bolt-i-dont-think-limits-words-of-inspiration-from-the-fastest-man-on-earth/articleshow/130841476.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/international-sports/quote-of-the-day-by-usain-bolt-i-dont-think-limits-words-of-inspiration-from-the-fastest-man-on-earth/articleshow/130841476.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-06T05:43:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Sports Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130841543,imgsize-108878.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Project Freedom will be paused for a short period': Trump halts Hormuz operation amid Iran talks, Pakistan request]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130841468.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump has halted 'Project Freedom,' a US military initiative to escort ships through the Strait of Hormuz, citing requests from Pakistan and progress toward a deal with Iran. This pause comes after the US declared the offensive phase of 'Operation Epic Fury' complete, emphasizing defensive actions in the region.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/project-freedom-will-be-paused-for-a-short-period-trump-halts-hormuz-operation-amid-iran-talks-pakistan-request/articleshow/130841468.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/project-freedom-will-be-paused-for-a-short-period-trump-halts-hormuz-operation-amid-iran-talks-pakistan-request/articleshow/130841468.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-06T05:25:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130841473,imgsize-29664.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Israeli beauty queen says she bumped into Zohran Mamdani's wife at a cafe, Rama Duwaji 'refused to engage']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130838939.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/israeli-beauty-queen-says-she-bumped-into-zohran-mamdanis-wife-at-a-cafe-rama-duwaji-refused-to-engage/articleshow/130838939.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/israeli-beauty-queen-says-she-bumped-into-zohran-mamdanis-wife-at-a-cafe-rama-duwaji-refused-to-engage/articleshow/130838939.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-06T02:20:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130838957,imgsize-61068.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[VTuber Filian vanishes online after months away, massive content wipe shocks fans]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130838907.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[VTuber Filian has vanished from all online platforms, including YouTube, Twitch, and TikTok, on May 1, 2026. This sudden content wipe, following a five-month absence, has sparked fan speculation about a potential rebranding, hiatus, or even a connection to past controversies regarding model rights. With no official statement